abstract: If New Hampshire moves it's primary to December, it could diminish the importance of winning the state.
snippet: If New Hampshire moves it's primary to December, it could diminish the importance of winning the state.
lead_paragraph: I've generally been of the view that the earlier that the Republican primaries and caucuses begin, the better off Mitt Romney's campaign will be.

headline.main: Early New Hampshire Primary Could Backfire on Romney
